North has
successfully fired such a
weapon.

08:00.914 --> 08:06.319 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The foreign ministers of China,
Japan, and
South Korea denounced the launch
today in

08:06.353 --> 08:08.722 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
