08:40.387 --> 08:44.357 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Dow Jones industrial average
lost nearly
66 points to close at 18481.

08:44.391 --> 08:47.994 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Nasdaq fell 42 points, and
the S&amp;P 500
dropped 11.

08:48.027 --> 08:52.399 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Still to come on
the "NewsHour":
Vice President Biden's visit to
Turkey amid

08:52.432 --> 08:58.471 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
