attacked from above,
as Turkish tanks and special
forces moved

09:30.637 --> 09:32.305 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
into the town.

09:32.338 --> 09:35.575 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Syrian rebel groups were also
part of the
operation.

09:35.608 --> 09:40.180 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
