main U.S.-backed
Syrian Kurdish militia, known as
the YPG,

09:48.388 --> 09:50.790 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
which has been taking over
territory from
ISIS.

09:50.824 --> 09:56.629 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
Vice President Biden was
visiting Turkey today,
and he called upon the Kurds to
limit their

09:56.663 --> 09:58.398 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
advances.

09:58.431 --> 10:00.500 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOSEPH BIDEN, Vice President of
the United
States: We have made it
absolutely clear to

10:00.533 --> 10:06.906 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the elements that were part of
