30:23.088 --> 30:24.756 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And we're committed to that.

30:24.790 --> 30:26.591 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The president is committed to
that.

30:26.625 --> 30:32.731 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There was a memorandum of
agreement between
the secretary and the
administration that

30:32.764 --> 30:34.099 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
she went in to.

30:34.132 --> 30:38.770 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
