the Foreign
Relations Committee.

30:38.804 --> 30:44.042 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And while we made one small
mistake, in my
judgment, in terms of what we
were supposed

30:44.076 --> 30:52.884 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
