30:53.919 --> 30:55.520 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Sure.

30:55.554 --> 30:58.857 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
DONNA SHALALA: But, more
importantly, what
