state.

31:02.794 --> 31:09.167 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have to take a much stronger
position to
eliminate any perception of
conflict of interests.

31:09.201 --> 31:11.002 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Right.

31:11.036 --> 31:13.605 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
I think that right now,
unfortunately, because
this is the political season,
the examples

31:13.638 --> 31:17.976 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
