you had access
to Mrs. Clinton.

31:45.437 --> 31:46.905 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And I think the concern is...

31:46.938 --> 31:52.110 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DONNA SHALALA: Well, I think we
