connection there.

32:03.355 --> 32:05.190 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
But here's what's important.

32:05.223 --> 32:10.495 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What's important to us is that
there are millions
of people around the world whose
lives are

32:10.529 --> 32:17.169 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
