32:18.670 --> 32:20.872 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We have to make sure that work
continues.

32:20.906 --> 32:24.643 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The president has reinvented
philanthropy
in this country.

32:24.676 --> 32:27.679 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
This is an extraordinary
foundation.

32:27.712 --> 32:36.822 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And no one in the foundation
wants to see
these attacks or in any way be
perceived as

32:36.855 --> 32:38.623 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
