37:23.608 --> 37:27.112 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: The local
council is working
hard to integrate the newcomers.

37:27.145 --> 37:31.483 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
