visiting to
help the family with temporary
citizenship

37:31.516 --> 37:36.821 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
documents that will enable them
to travel
freely throughout Europe.

37:36.855 --> 37:40.525 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Al-Mohammad is looking to get
off welfare
benefits and is seeking a
business partner

37:40.558 --> 37:42.393 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to set up a restaurant.

37:42.427 --> 37:46.131 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KHATTAB AL-MOHAMMAD: Although we
are -- appreciate
their help, but we want to
participate in

37:46.164 --> 37:49.234 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
this society and in the economy
of this country.

37:49.267 --> 37:53.638 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, we don't like to be living
on this kind
of charity.

37:53.671 --> 37:58.042 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I suppose all the Syrians
are trying their
best in the different places.

37:58.076 --> 38:01.079 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We are normally independent.

38:01.112 --> 38:04.048 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We don't like to be dependent on
someone.

38:04.082 --> 38:07.986 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator): I'm
very happy.

38:08.019 --> 38:09.654 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Icelanders are good people.

38:09.687 --> 38:12.690 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The country is very generous and
welcoming.

38:12.724 --> 38:16.761 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we are proud to be here and
to be part
of this country.

38:16.794 --> 38:19.764 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
BOY (through translator): I'm
happy here.

38:19.797 --> 38:21.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I have friends to play ball
with.

38:21.566 --> 38:24.569 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HALINA AL-MOHAMMAD, Syrian
Refugee (through
translator): Of course it's
better here, and

38:24.602 --> 38:25.703 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
secure.

38:25.737 --> 38:28.072 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
The living here is good,
especially the kids'
school.

38:28.106 --> 38:33.711 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Akureyri is a
bustling town
of 18,000 people, popular with
tourists for

38:33.745 --> 38:36.714 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
