nature pursuits.

38:36.748 --> 38:41.085 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The council is anxious to avoid
the mistakes
of much bigger countries, which
have created

38:41.119 --> 38:44.122 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
