40:06.137 --> 40:08.573 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But for the immediate future, we
are settling
here.

40:08.606 --> 40:09.741 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
This is good for the children.

40:09.774 --> 40:10.742 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
They feel safe here.

40:10.775 --> 40:12.844 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They will get an education.

40:12.877 --> 40:16.814 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
