53:17.694 --> 53:21.598 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Voyager, for example, just
leaving our solar
system, if you aimed it at this
newly discovered

53:21.632 --> 53:24.535 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
