70,000 years
to get there.

53:24.568 --> 53:27.805 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, that gives you an idea,
where it's not
just billions and billions.

53:27.838 --> 53:29.540 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We're talking trillions and
trillions here.

53:29.573 --> 53:33.077 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And to get a
